I"Ü<p>Good article here on bearings
<a href="https://www.bearingsexpress.com.au/buying/buying-guides/trailer-wheel-bearing-kits">https://www.bearingsexpress.com.au/buying/buying-guides/trailer-wheel-bearing-kits</a>.</p>

<p>In particular.</p>

<p><em>Holden Trailer Wheel Bearings</em> have a 11mm stud size</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Inner Bearings: Cone LM67048 Cup LM167010
(inches): 1.25
(mm):  31.75

Outer Bearings:  Cone LM11949 Cup LM11910
(inches):  0.75
(mm):  19.05
These bearings are commonly written as:
LM67048/10, and
LM11949/10
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><em>Ford Trailer Wheel Bearings</em> have a 12.4mm stud size</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Inner Bearings: Cone L68149 Cup L68110
(inches): 1.3775
(mm):  34.989
Outer Bearings:  Cone LM12749 Cup LM12710
(inches): 0.8656
(mm):  21.986
</code></pre></div></div>
